=Description=

"We envision an Africa where borders, be it physical, economic, or intellectual, do not limit the creative potential of the 900 Million young Africans.

In fact, an open, permissionless, and decentralized internet is the best platform to place Africans at the forefront of progress. We have unmatched scale, strong grit, and the context to build highly advanced economies with frontier technologies.

Borderless is a public goods initiative, building the blocks to make this vision a reality. It is founded by Yoseph Ayele, and supported by local and global communities."

